<h3>CSEM: Yellow Brick Road Introduction:</h3>
<h5>If you are taking this tour it is likely you are a new student studying one of the many fields available in the school of Computer Science, Engineering, and Mathematics. This tour is designed as a self guided way of becoming familiar with the classrooms you will be attending during your studies. QR codes have been provided around the IST and ENGR buildings to provide information about the tour including maps and other details. You can access the links to these pages using the buttons provided above as well. Additionally a link to the school's Twitter page is also provided. </h5>